                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220417-80-off402 t18220417-80-cd403"></join>, one handkerchief, value 4 s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18220417-80-victim746" type="victimName">
                        William Perfect 
                        Richards
