                     <interp inst="t18220417-80-person749" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was with Wilden, and am certain of both the prisoners.</p>
               <p>SABEY'S Defence. I was coming along, the gentleman turned round and said I had his handkerchief. I had my hands in my pocket at the time.</p>
               <p>SABEY - <rs id="t18220417-80-verdict406" type="verdictDescription">
